      <para>Extensions gives more possibility to test applications: it extends from existing protocols by importing services descriptions to test, it extends the test framework by implementing new test protocols. </para>
      <para>Extensions are versioned and can be installed by yourself.</para>
    </introduction>

    <!-- Add one or more top-level section elements.  These are collapsible.
